{
  "id": "RAW_af0a11aa",
  "title": "MiniMax M2.1，首个跨过“长程任务可用性阈值”的国产模型",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247500177&idx=1&sn=450243b8420fb40d7bcd9b78f3f81ab7",
  "date": "2025-12-26 10:19:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"padding: 20px 24px 56px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0px auto;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;background-color: rgb(250, 249, 247) !important;text-align: left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">前几天MiniMax发布了M2.1模型，朋友们催我测评。其实我已经测评了一周了，为什么迟迟没发布呢？因为这次我在用它做Raphael的一个新的大型功能。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raphael的这个新功能，我原本不敢用国产模型写。比较机缘巧合吧，因为功能有点太大了，我又嫌GPT-5.2-Codex太慢，发现MiniMax M2.1很快，就给了它机会。 结果，表现亮眼。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">先来一个省流版</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 24px;\">省流版</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">优点</span></span></p>\n   <ol style=\"margin: 32px 0px;padding-left: 32px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">长程任务(long-running tasks)能力有极大提升。长程任务能力，在国产模型中是很稀缺的，而</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">MiniMax M2.1可能是第一个跨过“长程任务可用性阈值”的国产模型</span><span leaf=\"\">，复杂任务终于不会写崩了。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">速度快</span><span leaf=\"\">。可以在较长时间内咔咔干活，吞吐量大。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“约束遵循”做得不错，相对来说不容易健忘。可能是和前面提到的“长程任务能力有提升”相关。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">前端审美能力</span><span leaf=\"\">不亚于Claude Sonnet 4.5，无论是Web、iOS、Android。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">包月套餐内包含“图片识别”和“网络搜索”的MCP工具。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">包月套餐首月只需要9.9元</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">M2.1广泛兼容Claude Code, Droid , Cline, Kilo Code, Roo Code等几乎一切编程Agent，且</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">Droid和M2.1是绝配</span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">M2.1是一款开源模型</span><span leaf=\"\">！就在刚刚！这是送给某些老外AI公司的圣诞节礼物吗？哈哈，一些美国公司的“自研”模型，又可以升级了。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">缺点</span></span></p>\n   <ol style=\"margin: 32px 0px;padding-left: 32px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">逻辑深度不够</span><span leaf=\"\">。遇到复杂的系统架构时，容易陷入死循环，并不能很好的理解全貌。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">有点急于求成</span><span leaf=\"\">。有时候会在尚未理清楚全部逻辑的时候就开始工作，做出来有点虎头蛇尾。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">缺点缓解方案：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 32px 0px;padding-left: 32px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">先帮它写好包含完整逻辑架构的SPEC，M2.1长程任务能力强，不怕你的SPEC长；</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">执行完成后，再让M2.1根据SPEC自我检查代码；</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于改动比较大的情况，我会让GPT-5.2-Codex再额外做一次代码审核。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">下面展开讲</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 24px;\">前端审美能力有明显的提升</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">刚才提到，我这次用MiniMax M2.1是做一个复杂任务 —— 给Raphael加无限画板(Infinite Canvas)。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">怎么样，还不错吧？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">有一种“达芬奇工作台”的感觉，不是一个纯白色、平板的主流Canvas画板。感觉M2.1的品味很不错。</span></p>\n   <table style=\"width: 100% !important;border-collapse: collapse !important;margin: 20px auto !important;table-layout: fixed !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016518\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5324074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8ae6a4de&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7sicMGGsAZvjocoedV4ITbuaWRtFpa3gn8PCdnLuicQECCgVB7IAx7eiabsKQibt2j4oF0VCPmvr15A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016520\" data-ratio=\"0.5287037037037037\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c4bb26b7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7sicMGGsAZvjocoedV4ITbORkPdPDjAetRZbOfYic6Q4gQ3Xdx2777ra3yibAiac2zYsp65WLKIwVqQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">尤其是下面那个悬浮的输入框，我很是喜欢。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我放大一点，看看细节。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016514\" data-ratio=\"0.4861111111111111\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12) 0px 8px 32px;max-height: 600px !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=917829e8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7sicMGGsAZvjocoedV4ITbiciaicCUcmpXjbfKY6U5tBaRRL90jSaalYHtM7ibM51nl1hVa69KKZkwGw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你喜欢看客观测评的话，也可参考这里。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">仅考虑前端能力，目前王者毫无疑问是Gemini 3 Pro，而M2.1和Claude Sonnet 4.5几乎是平手，也算是和国际顶级选手上同一张桌子吃饭了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016523\" data-ratio=\"0.30925925925925923\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=45e6cc77&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7sicMGGsAZvjocoedV4ITbzS0QrPCjK7zN9ZeKzicqLRhG5vGlMQ5XTZib35BldSKxIiaUMGGvB7VZw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding: 20px 24px 56px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0px auto;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;background-color: rgb(250, 249, 247) !important;text-align: left;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 24px;\">速度快</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding: 20px 24px 56px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0px auto;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;background-color: rgb(250, 249, 247) !important;text-align: left;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">下面的录屏是原速。速度还可以吧？这里面是包含了Thinking的，不是纯粹输出。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016527\" data-ratio=\"0.6111111111111112\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b236b39b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2F607DKnuWzlG7sicMGGsAZvjocoedV4ITbBxjgaicXBiatkCoF2ro5wk4C0FGxLgGDxa8lAWVUZ00B65nnGK0Qzd8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 24px;\">为什么推荐Droid</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">一句话总结： Droid + M2.1 ≈ Droid + Claude Sonnet 4.5。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在Droid框架加持下的M2.1，是最能够平替Claude Sonnet 4.5的靠谱选择。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">注意：这不是用模型去刷题、刷榜，而是：模型 + Agent 框架组合后的“真实工程完成能力”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016515\" data-ratio=\"0.26944444444444443\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12) 0px 8px 32px;max-height: 600px !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7faf157a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7sicMGGsAZvjocoedV4ITb9XJibvEP7E2QvzRjttgjYRibJmjo6EP5AB4MqFaqcxBC93pu7MZwWibcg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 24px;\">长程任务能力是怎么回事？</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude/Codex系列模型早在今年Q2就开始卷长程任务能力，我们经常看到说它们能够“独自工作好几个小时”，这个能力国内模型暂时都不拥有。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">先跟各位朋友做一个简单的科普 —— “长程任务”(Long-running Tasks)跟“长上下文”（Long Context）是两码事。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 32px 0px;padding-left: 32px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">长上下文 是你能一次性读完一本书；</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">长程任务 是你能读完书，写出代码，运行报错了自己查文档，查完文档改代码，改完代码再跑测试，周而复始，直到全部完成完成，全程可以持续几小时甚至几十小时，给人一种“自主打工”的感觉。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我非常喜欢让我的AI牛马能够“自主打工”，总是喜欢琢磨如何让它们能够干得更久。我在十字路口博客也分享过一些心得和经验 。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;text-align: left;background-color: rgb(250, 249, 247) !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247498933&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=fa72632c3ed7141c0dfd6069f53e2cf0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"揭秘 Claude Code 榜一大哥：一个 AI 创业者如何把工具用到极致｜对话刘小排\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-style: italic;\">揭秘 Claude Code 榜一大哥：一个 AI 创业者如何把工具用到极致｜对话刘小排</span></a></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">遗憾的是，国产模型从来都不具备这项能力。 国产模型之前的通病是 \"Error Accumulation\"（误差累积），即多轮对话后智商断崖式下跌，因此无法生成长程任务。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">有人说，2025年的编程语言，排名第一的是“用中文回答”，排名第二是“你怎么又忘了？？”，原因正是如此。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">MiniMax M2.1 在这方面有显著改善，让我看到了一点点的曙光。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然MiniMax M2.1的长程任务能力不足以连续工作好几小时，但是</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">连续工作十几分钟，是比较容易做到的。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;padding: 20px 24px 56px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0px auto;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;background-color: rgb(250, 249, 247) !important;text-align: left;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">如果你想感受一下长程任务，可以参考我之前的文章<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247499915&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=3c27ef4939e22a9cf8ac1a8781a79ddf&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"复杂需求如何让AI一次写对？面对复杂需求，这是我实战沉淀的Vibe Coding终极SOP\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-style: italic;\">复杂需求如何让AI一次写对？面对复杂需求，这是我实战沉淀的Vibe Coding终极SOP</span></a></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 24px;\">上难度测试：MiniMax M2.1的逻辑深度问题，略微欠缺</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">先让MiniMax M2.1自己写完代码，它真的很快完成了，根据我预先提供的需求说明。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是一个典型的长程任务，一共修改了41个文件，除去多语言文件，也有9个文件之多，同时包含多个页面的前端、后端、数据库逻辑。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我先让M2.1自己审核一遍代码，再让GPT-5.2-Codex(xhigh)审核了一遍。</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">“ 审核我们尚未提交的代码,提出意见”。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016517\" data-ratio=\"0.512962962962963\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 48px auto;border-radius: 12px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.12) 0px 8px 32px;max-height: 600px !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=301be4f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7sicMGGsAZvjocoedV4ITbIbld0grfL9BBibXgDQPQpQ2DGBPzrQG4D5iabzYxrHZ1mgM5rZJwhALw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">认真看完两者的结论，</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">发现MiniMax M2.1看得不够细，缺乏逻辑深度</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。详见下面两个截图</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先：MiniMax M2.1认为最严重的问题是“30种语言翻译键缺失”，这是错误的，实际上我们有32种语言，全部都已经翻译好了，不存在缺失问题。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后：有一些更严重的问题没有发现。“参考图丢失”才是最严重的问题，这个问题，GPT-5.2-Codex(xhigh)发现了。</span></p>\n   <table style=\"width: 100% !important;border-collapse: collapse !important;margin: 20px auto !important;table-layout: fixed !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016516\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.787962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=66ade170&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7sicMGGsAZvjocoedV4ITbGVic7lbxqD7uApQOePwrByrPaCB4bv09jxQgoPqOhU3FeiawYTsGdnKA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016519\" data-ratio=\"1.0666666666666667\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=22ec2521&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlG7sicMGGsAZvjocoedV4ITbO99AJjojQUdJhKibJeB1ToIyV63HNzmCxQXNv8cNIk6QqgeUpq2r9og%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 24px;\">总评</span></span></strong></p>\n   <ol style=\"margin: 32px 0px;padding-left: 32px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">MiniMax M2.1 可能是第一个跨过“长程任务可用性阈值”的国产编程模型。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用Droid + M2.1完成去完成真实任务，是接近Claude Sonnet 4.5平替的选择。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">M2.1干活很快。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">M2.1美中不足是逻辑深度问题，需要想办法补齐。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 16px 0px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;text-align: left;font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">包月套餐首月只要9.9元</span><span leaf=\"\">，值得支持。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 32px 0px !important;line-height: 1.75 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">期待国产模型越来越好！ 咱们评论区见。</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "MiniMax M2.1 模型在长程编程任务中展现出跨越式进步，尤其在前端审美和执行速度上表现亮眼，但仍需在逻辑深度上改进。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "MiniMax M2.1 模型在长程编程任务中展现出跨越式进步，尤其在前端审美和执行速度上表现亮眼，但仍需在逻辑深度上改进。",
  "summary": "作者刘小排分享了对 MiniMax M2.1 模型的深度测评体验，主要围绕其在复杂编程任务（长程任务）中的表现。文章指出，M2.1 是首个跨越“长程任务可用性阈值”的国产模型，能够连续工作十几分钟，而非此前国产模型普遍存在的“误差累积”问题。作者在为其 Raphael 项目新增“无限画板”功能时，发现 M2.1 在前端审美、执行速度和与 Agent 框架（如 Droid）的结合方面表现亮眼，可作为 Claude Sonnet 4.5 的平替。文章也坦诚指出了 M2.1 的不足，即逻辑深度不够，在处理复杂系统架构时容易陷入死循环，且有时会急于求成。作者根据实践经验，提供了缓解这些缺点的方案，如预先提供详细 SPEC 等。最后，文章总结了 M2.1 的优缺点，并鼓励支持国产模型的发展。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "MiniMax M2.1 在国产模型中首次实现“长程任务可用性阈值”，显著提升了处理复杂编程任务的能力。",
      "explanation": "国产模型此前普遍存在“误差累积”导致多轮对话后智商下降的问题，M2.1 能够连续工作十几分钟而保持稳定，是其在编程模型领域的重要突破。"
    },
    {
      "point": "M2.1 在前瞻审美、执行速度和与 Agent 框架结合方面表现出色，可作为国际顶级模型（如 Claude Sonnet 4.5）的有效平替。",
      "explanation": "作者实测 M2.1 为 Raphael 项目开发无限画板功能时，对其生成的前端界面设计、快速响应能力以及与 Droid 等 Agent 框架的兼容性表示认可，尤其指出“Droid + M2.1”组合在真实工程项目中的实用性。"
